column16: Asdrubal Cabrera flies out to left fielder Rajai Davis.
Jason Kipnis singles on a line drive to right fielder J.  D.   Martinez.   Yan Gomes scores.
Ryan Raburn grounds into a double play, second baseman Ian Kinsler to shortstop Eugenio Suarez to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.   Yan Gomes to 3rd.    David Murphy out at 2nd.
David Murphy singles on a ground ball to right fielder J.   Martinez.   Nick Swisher scores.    Yan Gomes to 2nd.
Yan Gomes singles on a line drive to right fielder J.  D.   Martinez.   Nick Swisher to 3rd.
Nick Swisher doubles (17) on a fly ball to center fielder Austin Jackson.   Lonnie Chisenhall scores.
Carlos Santana grounds out softly to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Michael Brantley grounds out to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Asdrubal Cabrera lines out to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
With Asdrubal Cabrera batting, David Murphy caught stealing 2nd base, catcher Bryan Holaday to shortstop Eugenio Suarez.
Jason Kipnis flies out to left fielder Rajai Davis in foul territory.
Ryan Raburn flies out to left fielder Rajai Davis.
Yan Gomes grounds out, shortstop Eugenio Suarez to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Nick Swisher called out on strikes.
With Lonnie Chisenhall batting, Michael Brantley picked off and caught stealing 3rd base, catcher Bryan Holaday to shortstop Eugenio Suarez to third baseman Nick Castellanos.
Carlos Santana walks.   Michael Brantley to 2nd.
Michael Brantley singles on a bunt ground ball to pitcher Drew VerHagen.
